{"tid":1077965,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV 《綠豆》班底拍新劇《歎息橋》","createTime":"2019-03-26T03:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T02:17:48.000Z","uid":15213,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5094f59212c474e2dc9665f54631755ddf5732c8","tid":1077965,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"上星期公佈咗冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日出咗teaser:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fatballslim/videos/10156251052269632/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffatballslim%2Fvideos%2F10156251052269632%2F&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqxA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=590d092b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fatballslim/videos/10156251052269632/</a><br />\n<br />\n林保怡 周家怡 衛詩雅 陳奐仁 主演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林保怡做埋監製<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《綠豆》Fatball &amp; 25 導演 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲見到有秦沛 伍姑娘 郭鋒 銘sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有新血岑珈其 談善言 陸駿光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不得了組合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後仲要冇南方舞廳份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddfa9ae09538d860d43017380e766af34ed6ba3","tid":1077965,"uid":15213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>【歎息橋】粉碎與ViuTV不和傳聞　林保怡：關係好到一年食一次飯</strong><br />\n<br />\n拍攝這劇集Bowie直言很希望觀眾觀看完能接收到思考人生及做人的訊息：「希望大家有『維他命』袋入袋，睇完呢部劇裡面角色，會思考人生，睇會唔會有類似自己相似嘅性格，衛詩雅就有呢個情況，佢拍完都話真係曾經諗過咁做。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林保怡周家怡新劇不再是一對<br />\n劇本內容也比較複雜，導演25與Fatball直言，劇集播出後應該會給觀眾責罵，不過保怡完全不擔心：「其實一定會有人鬧，因為每一部電影就算幾差都好，實有人喜歡，多方面意見都會聽，尤其是第一次做監製。」<br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: orange;\">今次Bowie將不會再續與周家怡在《綠豆》的愛情，預告投向衛詩雅的擁抱</span>。劇情指，飾演李子勇（Thomas）的林保怡，出生貧窮，年輕時為了賺取母親的醫藥費，拼命打工賺錢，認識了同在茶餐廳打工的少女、由周家怡飾演的方小薇（Sammy），自此成了好朋友。Thomas母離世後，他開了一間餐應，生意不俗，與好友兼拍檔Sammy一起打拼。<br />\n<br />\n一天，Thomas重遇在比利時結識、由衛詩雅飾演的何樂兒（Joyce），二人一拍即合，很快便走在一起。與此同時Joyce與胡啟源（陳奐仁飾）亦已拍拖8年。四人關係撲朔迷離。他們在一個喪禮上重遇，終於明白四人之間二十多年來的糾纏要如何作結。<br />\n<br />\n(內有少少劇透）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/307970/歎息橋-粉碎與viutv不和傳聞-林保怡-關係好到一年食一次飯\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F307970%2F%E6%AD%8E%E6%81%AF%E6%A9%8B-%E7%B2%89%E7%A2%8E%E8%88%87viutv%E4%B8%8D%E5%92%8C%E5%82%B3%E8%81%9E-%E6%9E%97%E4%BF%9D%E6%80%A1-%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E9%A3%AF&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqxA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=650ea86a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/307970/歎息橋-粉碎與viutv不和傳聞-林保怡-關係好到一年食一次飯</a>"},{"pid":"ee8b8eb70a2e6fdcf93f41f937033d300846a490","tid":1077965,"uid":15213,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"劇名用書法字勁靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tYcjm4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYcjm4E.jpg&h=f36c17cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Kz2jRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Kz2jRk.jpg&h=0db70488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zpkdrwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZpkdrwn.jpg&h=00a4bdd6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddCWph1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddCWph1.jpg&h=40685c42&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YNhZ6wn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYNhZ6wn.jpg&h=1b896ca2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid"