/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3caf49c7ee704f60e6694ab6241ff5b6a27567","tid":1077965,"uid":73103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:20:50.000Z","msg":"潘燦良先係真正主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50cb0812213add7f2bc0ff309dc2745c8a12860","tid":1077965,"uid":51288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fdb9011eed20d4a3970d7a2f10b0967c79a249b","tid":1077965,"uid":2811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"無潘燦良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"有呀 佢有客串嘛。"},{"pid":"51f882e7c73139dbda42e8c40eb5af50d241d74d","tid":1077965,"uid":15213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"今次編劇都係搵寫綠豆嘅黃綺琳<br />\n完全飛起咗南廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1afbb00ac56879f73213512ff215fc02fc2db59","tid":1077965,"uid":26274,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"嘆息橋（義大利語：Ponte dei Sospiri）是位於義大利威尼斯聖馬可廣場附近，總督府側面的一座巴洛克風格的石橋。在運河水道上有幾條橋，而此條嘆息橋是密封式拱橋建築，由內向外望只能通過橋上的小窗子。嘆息橋的兩端連接法院與監獄兩處，死囚通過此橋之時，常是行刑前的一刻，因感嘆即將結束的人生而得名；是威尼斯最著名的橋樑之一。"},{"pid":"7ab06898d14336d3746814688b219d3920b01237","tid":1077965,"uid":69695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"幾時有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7616da80830d2731d1495878259e54f879607deb","tid":1077965,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"南方舞廳先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccb7d7e3de807c5650f8de9af6049bfadca39dc","tid":1077965,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7616da80830d2731d1495878259e54f879607deb","tid":1077965,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci